{"h1dc60598g9998g401fg96dagd045508baf6e": ["If I don't see you after the battle... tell the children I took out the drow.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "ec3a0123-0d66-11ba-4371-0e1990e3d5aa"], "ha1bab19eg2720g419fg8a84ga7f2d3992349": ["Get that damn gate closed!", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "eb8efb66-be04-b74f-4b2a-5daa2df90077"], "hc928780ag5429g45c8g972cgb3ec872abf05": ["This is it, people. Weapons ready, eyes to the front. ", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "b81cb1b9-d7ee-bcd1-7e9d-e34fbd072be3"], "hef2ef521g1e69g4082gac9ag2e0b607fda74": ["Anyone who takes down a worg gets their choice of cut tonight...", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "889b135b-468e-4c3b-2d51-45e6ef9dc3b3"], "ha1bab7a2g33d4g4a20ga3fbgd31e522bdf73": ["... by Amaunator's Eternal Sun, none of us are dying today!", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "af6f6673-cd91-47f5-8857-3a32973092df"], "h36249f31gb3acg4dbegba32g5c3ed7de8736": ["*A splinter of ice works its way into your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "bd0aa9e5-e4f1-c336-d88b-c9b69f038043"], "hacbce0a3g2c44g44cdgaedeg5466d7901bb5": ["<i>A pretty speech. It almost brings a tear to my eye. </i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "e0a3ab1d-b204-fea5-95b3-8c9eaa8fb02d"], "h86d7010dgc17dg48c0g8238g4f492438c590": ["<i>Now slit his throat, and open that gate. The Absolute wants all of them dead.</i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "08295635-5110-9994-4f8a-b7722f35fd62"], "h38f62cbag870cg420dga6b7g12b334b6f04e": ["<i>Obey and open the gate.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "0e85fc6b-ac4b-51e7-e01b-7a150d386022"], "h0f5c2167g90aeg4ceega757g671d0b3f59d0": ["Traitor! The Blade now comes for <i>you.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "ac7118c3-8bef-02b2-8962-1e44e7fefc2a"], "h4c6fde66gcbf1g41d2g998dgb1956ef3c0a8": ["Oh, hells.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "73452f94-44b9-96af-d407-5d8690e59e5a"], "hf56f1a64ge96cg4e79g8cb8g08bf4293fbd7": ["You're in league with the damned drow?", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "07671f1e-847c-2d86-6d5a-80d7577305f1"], "h69f90e3bg7b54g42ddg903egc2d4615ace47": ["You're siding with that monster against your own people?", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "07671f1e-847c-2d86-6d5a-80d7577305f1"], "h9f7a7bedg4347g469agb371g1d1f017ea30d": ["It's nothing personal.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "42187d36-2af4-d70f-1c0f-92784417187f"], "h2b3463edg6494g4ab0g8e3agdc5e0d5e1911": ["Nothing personal? You betrayed us!", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "2eebffee-94bf-f434-40a2-d328a54ee60a"], "hc2b79fa9g6480g4f7cg8400g3abe122cf91f": ["Nothing personal? You betrayed us!", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "fe6beb1d-5fda-b69a-08eb-dbabce7b53e1"], "hf5632674g5180g490cga324g41d83e10db6d": ["At least you'll die before the goblins find the children.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "6c0706d5-e224-b22d-8093-c397007a32fe"], "hfe4317fagd0abg45f9g9e48g55f8d38ef4e5": ["You <i>monster</i>!", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "ff89ebf5-2b7c-1263-6bb8-6f084a2dcb0f"], "h71817505g77cdg4b83gba42g287560e0fe12": ["Oh gods...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "c402bdb7-ec44-1acb-b301-9164887bb90c"], "he78bd14fg4a48g4cb7g8270ga8a2a3e3de29": ["I'm truly sorry. I need healing - and the drow and her god are my best chance.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "12dcd4b5-6583-32a2-b276-037e2e3020dd"], "haa16333dg1c0bg4b4ag8ae8g65a7240eca60": ["Impspit!", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "3d92d564-4103-4c91-3364-e61424b044c1"], "h5e25c23cg8710g4657gbc5bgd5e94a071551": ["You're mad. How did I not see it?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "310b266f-96ee-9376-0b72-d7e1934c1a99"], "h168daeb2gbae0g4080gb738g2d52285dd089": ["Obviously.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "2d6ceace-edb5-c4f3-429e-efda7109a725"], "h2887fe3eg6f47g4330g9c29g5cbad5e6c638": ["Gods forgive me... I've doomed them all.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "28d46899-649c-ee89-9464-939eee83b342"], "h77ad310ag0578g4468gbc3egbae8da14b274": ["My people? I'm loyal only to myself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "18635578-464c-bb22-cf2a-f8e52e7c2541"], "h989105bcg1a82g4a2fg93a2g587d86f13d89": ["You'll burn in the Hells for this.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "d1710571-143b-19eb-6151-33b4d1776d29"], "h29907969g4069g47e0g8d0dg2cb8f40957f1": ["You <i>bastard</i>.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "34a63d76-0d17-8324-9429-194ca2369676"], "h42e69febgbee7g409fga3cbg34c1d71d87e3": ["What are you doing? They'll kill us all...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "fe6fcfac-f272-330b-110f-8fda61383af7"], "h0a68a593g8926g4a82g8cd5gb84206dbcfba": ["... hells. You're <i>with</i> them, aren't you?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "ed65831f-3997-1d5f-6385-0e110f6eedf1"], "hfb68b802g497cg4a51g95f7g70a9106eacce": ["... hells. You're siding <i>with</i> them, against your own people?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "ed65831f-3997-1d5f-6385-0e110f6eedf1"], "h466f2a01g08e0g4db5g886egeeb63980cdd1": ["No. This grove is under my protection.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "e5e84cb4-6d8c-b35b-9dec-58ed264aef1a"], "h068633c3g748ag421dg81fbge3243657093f": ["<i>Traitor! You think you can stand against me </i>and<i> the Absolute? </i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "07735f95-e34e-0827-d758-652ef5f7513d"], "h4cf56df3gd7e7g4f06g837agccdab38f26d2": ["<i>I'll dissect you.</i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "099531ba-2b22-4d27-30b2-b2d15f422358"], "h0e62cfddge562g4902g9c5fgb9cdae8429ea": ["Your god has no power here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "78823f71-dd0d-5a10-abde-c8745ae0e487"], "hd3d81818g3175g49fbgaef7g105d9f53e1f2": ["<i>You cower behind a doomed god when the Absolute promised you such power?</i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "f6c79467-c0a6-3794-888a-bf4ea7ab1479"], "h00474d72g56f8g41b3g8c71ge2628730a6b8": ["<i>You will die here. And your god will die with you.</i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "294a59e4-6088-740e-3514-085a40e5b73c"], "h984dba1ag17dag4fd5g8be0gdf92df2f52d4": ["New plan - I tear out <i>your</i> throat.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "c11057e5-dbdd-87d3-88c2-892b5e65a3d5"], "hafc9ade5g80c0g4165g9e3ag706f1fbe0141": ["No thanks. I've developed a taste for drow.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "7cb61b75-2532-e083-47ae-829f7e652cb6"], "h5923fc00gcf5dg42e0g927cgc0a55aa9dcef": ["There's been a change of plan.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "d5cdc9d5-194f-c34c-d950-466324010bad"], "hc337de47gdf9fg4ce3ga681g463a519cbd27": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "48d214be-ec5d-5382-0316-996082acb140"], "hdc610bfcg66c7g4eddga8c3g1d619d161459": ["I serve Shar, not the Absolute. The gate stays closed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "2514288c-728a-928e-61eb-f09216337afa"], "hb5621e64g59e3g4514gbf34g15bb3113ddb4": ["Not so fast. You've just walked into my trap.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "70b062c9-e60a-af26-966a-91dccc86dbe2"], "hfd4e5f56g8a72g4c5bgbdbdg56842051134a": ["These people are under my protection - but I'll see you in the Hells.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "2a0cafa2-09d1-05cb-8b32-377b201a0fbe"], "h8dcee4a2g4a03g4abdg9362g73392d4eda1c": ["Of course - as does my god.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "6bd63ed3-e332-9a1a-4b2a-ac637e5e1e4d"], "he1c2df16g6b66g461bg849cg0f7462f6c6b4": ["No. I'll show the Absolute the power of a <i>true</i> god.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "15f65f46-af85-4b7a-5b67-d0bbe93e83bf"], "h79389be9g6fa1g4f28ga82cg2eae33c0cc3c": ["This place belongs to Silvanus - the Absolute has no power here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "822b6bf2-3436-5115-0622-c68b8d488e00"], "h65895a08g688cg4bcbgae6bg455fe8478ef0": ["<i>Sacred? It is filth. It will burn, and you will burn with it</i>.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "64602197-8486-44fd-5a14-aa5ac94432e2"], "h69881b25geaa7g450cg8f04gf8633800d68f": ["Get that damn gate closed!", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "12492114-853e-c8b4-7cd9-94fa1d629f5a"], "h8b0c3fdbga3cdg4c2dg8a50g0bd8a1a39c92": ["I know that you are all afraid... but I also know that you have been fighting your whole lives.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "6928012f-eb78-fa03-489c-f278a4c675d2"], "h646e999fg9576g49a5gb725g91ce647566e5": ["We have never been handed the easy choices, or the gentle paths. And this is no different.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "1d159cd1-93e4-db54-9cd8-fd02baa441be"], "h6bfca205g592cg4c51g9e98gbff149c2e27b": ["These creatures would take our lives, our children... our future. And we must <i>resist</i>!", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "444cdf69-821c-4c18-e41e-1ea12c42e2e7"], "hcce0d021g8062g470ega0c1g8f8afbb6c609": ["This is it. Everything turns on this.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_RaidersArriveBeforeFight.html", "b28a4376-1468-bf34-3a3b-04d3c4845483"]}